Debrid,Link,is,a,downloader,and,seedbox,host,for,downloading,files,stored,on,filehosters,and,for,exchanging,information,using,the,BitTorrent,protocol,across,remote,servers,This,torrent,application,can,be,accessed,to,service,fast,downloads,and,is,compatible,with,many,filehosters,Using,the,Debrid,Link,RESTful,API,developers,can,command,POST,and,GET,HTTP,requests,to,programmatically,access,seedboxes,and,create,torrent,applications,Specific,API,calls,can,be,made,to,return,user,information,manage,and,retrieve,torrents,and,data,within,the,seedbox,access,the,downloader,to,manage,links,and,receive,traffic,information,interact,with,the,Debrid,link,forum,and,more,The,result,of,each,API,request,is,returned,in,JSON,format,Based,in,France,Debrid,Link,charges,a,monthly,subscription,for,API,usage,with,free,testing,included